title: Student Council
teacher: Mrs. Brar, Ms. Gonsales, Ms. Wong
purpose: We create a space that allows students to have a chance to lead and collaborate to further build a positive school environment and culture. We promote positive school activities and host fun spirit events! We promote spirit within the school.
typicalWeek: Every week theres something new! We brainstorm, plan, and organize school spirit events. We work as a team to create a fun and enthusiastic school environment by sharing ideas with with the team. We turn ideas into actions!
schedule: We meet on Tuesdays at Lunchtime. Come Join us!
